headline: Fifth Third Lights Up Hyper-Fast Electric Vehicle Chargers at Florida Branch
summary: CINCINNATI, November 12, 2024--Fifth Third Bank continues its historic clean energy progress today by introducing hyper-fast electric vehicle (EV) chargers for the first time at one of its banking centers. Fifth Third is making six hyper-fast charging stations publicly available at its eTown location in Jacksonville, Florida to better serve current EV owners and those considering transitioning to an EV.
